metadata.description:
For the first time in history, a PAPAYA will travel to the moon.

Spacial mission NOVA-C IM-1 powered by NASA and SPACE X, Launch in June 2023 

Alejandro Glatt has been selected as one of the 222 worldwide artists to represent Mexico and showcase art in the first ever art museum in the moon, “Lunaprise”

This AI art generative collection honors the launch of the FIRST PAPAYA IN THE MOON! 

https://www.intuitivemachines.com/im-1
